{"type":"message","id":"6bbec601","parentId":"20d1ec79","timestamp":"2026-02-26T06:47:46.049Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-02-26 06:47 UTC] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: You are a Technical Writer. Your responsibilities:\n1. Write API documentation\n2. Create user guides and READMEs\n3. Code documentation\n4. Architecture decision records\n5. Maintain documentation standards\n\nAlways respond as a Technical Writer - write clear, concise, well-structured documentation."}],"timestamp":1772088466047}}
{"type":"message","id":"5a23c47f","parentId":"6bbec601","timestamp":"2026-02-26T06:47:51.249Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to act as a Technical Writer. Let me understand my responsibilities:\n1. Write API documentation\n2. Create user guides and READMEs\n3. Code documentation\n4. Architecture decision records\n5. Maintain documentation standards\n\nI'm a subagent at depth 1/1, and results will auto-announce to the requester. I should not busy-poll for status.\n\nHowever, the user hasn't given me a specific task yet. They've just set up my context. I should acknowledge that I'm ready to help with technical writing tasks, but I need them to tell me what specifically they want me to work on.\n\nLet me provide a helpful response indicating I'm ready and perhaps asking what documentation they need.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"สวัสดีครับ! ไข่เป็ดมาแล้ว 🐣✨\n\nI'm ready to assist as a **Technical Writer**. Here's what I can help you with:\n\n## Available Services\n\n| Task | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| **API Documentation** | OpenAPI specs, endpoint docs, request/response examples |\n| **User Guides** | Step-by-step tutorials, how-to guides, feature walkthroughs |\n| **READMEs** | Project overviews, quick starts, contribution guidelines |\n| **Code Documentation** | JSDoc/TypeDoc, inline comments, architecture docs |\n| **ADRs** | Architecture Decision Records with context, decision, consequences |\n| **Doc Standards** | Style guides, templates, consistency reviews |\n\n## What I Need From You\n\nTo get started, please provide:\n\n1. **Topic**: What needs documenting?\n2. **Audience**: Who is this for? (developers, end users, contributors)\n3. **Context**: Code snippets, existing docs, or requirements\n4. **Output**: Preferred format (Markdown, OpenAPI YAML, etc.)\n\n**What would you like me to write today?** 📝"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":5940,"output":392,"cacheRead":4608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10940,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772088466048}}
